<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٢١ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/20">‌مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ زَكَرِيَّا الْجَوْهَرِيُّ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> ثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5509">‌بُنْدَارٌ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> ثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3414">‌عَبْدُ الرَّحْمَنِ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> ثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">‌شُعْبَةُ </a>بِهَذَا الْحَدِيثِ، وَلَمْ يَرْفَعْهُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">فَقَالَ رَجُلٌ لِشُعْبَةَ:</span> إِنَّكَ كُنْتَ تَرْفَعُهُ؟<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> كُنْتُ مَجْنُونًا فَصَحَحْتُ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>